videos.headline: Washington State strikes first with 12-yard TD pass
videos.description: Luke Falk connects with Jamal Morrow who scores a 12-yard touchdown to give the Cougars the lead.

videos.headline: Martin Jr.  hauls in long pass to move Cougars down the field
videos.description: Luke Falk finds Tavares Martin Jr. down the field and completes a 52-yard pass to put Washington State in the red zone.

videos.headline: Washington State extends lead on shovel-pass TD
videos.description: James Williams takes the shovel pass from Luke Falk and finds his way to the end zone for a 13-yard score.

videos.headline: Cougars score on a  40-yard catch a run
videos.description: Luke Falk dumps it to Tavares Martin Jr. who runs it to the house to stretch Washington State's lead.

videos.headline: Falk connects with Dimry for a 45-yard gain
videos.description: Washington State's CJ Dimry catches a pass from Luke Falk and adds a run to move the Cougars into the red zone.

videos.headline: Washington State tacks on 1-yard TD
videos.description: James Williams runs it in from the one-yard line for a Cougars touchdown which angers the defense.

videos.headline: Cornwell picked off by Washington State defense
videos.description: David Cornwell targets the end zone and his pass is picked off by Jalen Thompson giving the ball back to the Cougars.

videos.headline: Falk throws 4th touchdown pass against Nevada
videos.description: Luke Falk finds Jamire Calvin who dives in to the end zone for a touchdown to extend Washington's State's lead.

videos.headline: Falk shows off big arm with deep pass to Bell
videos.description: Luke Falk find Renard Bell way down field and completes a 60-yard pass that puts Washington State in scoring position.

videos.headline: Martin Jr. dives for the pylon getting a Washington State TD
videos.description: Luke Falk completes a 19-yard pass to Tavares Martin Jr. who dives and hits the pylon resulting in a Cougar touchdown.
